## 6. Database

### SQLite DB Location
- Local: `./data/monitor.db` (default)
- Container: `/data/monitor.db` (PVC-mounted)

### Inspect Database
```bash
sqlite3 ./data/monitor.db
.tables
.schema launches
SELECT count(*) FROM launches;
SELECT count(*) FROM test_items;
```

---

## 7. Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| `MODULE_NOT_FOUND` | Run `npm install` |
| SQLite errors | Check `DB_PATH` directory exists |
| RP API 401 | Check `REPORTPORTAL_TOKEN` |
| Slack not sending | Check `SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL` is set |
| Port in use | Change `DASHBOARD_PORT` |

### Clean Reinstall
```bash
rm -rf node_modules dist
npm install
npm run build
```

